       <h2>尋妖誌：島嶼妖怪文化之旅</h2>\n                <div class=\"layout_book\">\n                    <div>\n                        <img class=\"book \" src=\"../assets/book1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bookcontent\">\n                        <p>透過台灣民俗與生活記憶中有關妖怪傳說的記憶，採取行旅與踏查的方式尋找台灣妖怪的足跡，其中規劃十一條走訪妖怪的路線，將口傳或文獻所載的妖怪一一揭露其神祕面相，提供可實際按圖索驥的便利性，並搭配行程中的小旅行，但最後呼籲，島嶼千年靈氣，妖怪法力高強，懇請膽小者勿試！\n                        </p>\n                        <div class=\"row mt-3 mt-sm-1 pt-3 pt-sm-0\">\n\n                            <a class=\"col-5\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/morningstarpublishing\" target=\"blank\">\n                                <img src=\"../assets/晨星出版社.png\" alt=\"\">\n                            </a>\n                            <a class=\"col-7\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TPE.Legend\" target=\"blank\">\n                                <img src=\"../assets/台北異文地方工作室.png\" alt=\"\">\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"row mt-3\">\n                            <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aYbCC2\" target=\"blank\"> <img class=\"col-5\" src=\"../assets/buy.jpg\"\n                                    alt=\"\"> </a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"layout_sort\">\n                <h2>唯妖論：臺灣神怪本事</h2>\n                <div class=\"layout_book\">\n                    <div>\n                        <img class=\"book\" src=\"../assets/book2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bookcontent\">\n\n                        <p>重新認識臺灣的過程中，最缺乏的一塊就是臺灣的妖怪神異文化。本書考察了49個臺灣妖怪神異，每個妖怪神異都包含：繪師重新賦予他們的圖像＋現代版極短篇故事＋詳盡的文獻與田野資料！讓妖怪神異與現代生活緊密相連。\n                        </p>\n                        <div class=\"row mt-5 mt-sm-1\">\n                            <a class=\"col-5\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kiwifruitstudio\" target=\"blank\"> <img\n                                    src=\"../assets/奇異果文創.png\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n                            <a class=\"col-7\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TPE.Legend\" target=\"blank\"> <img\n                                    src=\"../assets/台北異文地方工作室.png\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"row mt-3 mb-5 \">\n                            <a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010730758\" target=\"blank\"> <img class=\"col-5\"\n                                    src=\"../assets/buy.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n\n\n\n</template>\n\n<script>\nexport default {\n    data() {\n        return {\n            title: '意猶未盡？瞭解更多',\n            newsInfo: [],\n        }\n    },\n\n    mounted() {\n        // eslint-disable-next-line no-undef\n        axios\n            .get('https://ftvnews-api2.azurewebsites.net/API/FtvGetNewsWeb.aspx?Cate=民俗月&Page=1&sp=6')\n            .then((response) => {\n                // console.log(response)\n                let data = response.data.ITEM\n                data.forEach((item) => {\n                    this.newsInfo.push(item)\n                })\n            })\n            .catch((error) => {\n                console.log('error' + error)\n            })\n    },\n}\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.layout {\n    background-image: url(../assets/b3.png);\n    background-size: cover;\n    font-family: '華康愛情體W5';\n    max-height: 100%;\n\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n    .section_news {\n        min-height: 2200px;\n    }\n}\n\n\npicture {\n    max-width: 400px;\n    min-height: 300px;\n    display: block;\n    margin: auto;\n}\n\nh4 {\n    display: -webkit-box;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    text-overflow: ellipsis;\n    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;\n    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;\n    line-height: 30px;\n    max-height: 70px;\n    padding: 0 0.3rem;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\n.layout_grid div div:nth-last-child(1) a {\n    display: inline;\n    padding: 0.3rem;\n    border: 1px solid;\n}\n\n.layout_grid p {\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin: 1rem auto;\n}\n\n.layout_grid {\n    max-width: 1000px;\n}\n\n.layout_content {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n    grid-gap: 2.5rem;\n\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {\n    .layout_content {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n\n    }\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n    .layout_content {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n        padding: 0rem 3rem\n    }\n}\n\n\n\n.container {\n\n    margin: auto;\n    overflow-y: hidden;\n\n\n}\n\n.news {\n    height: 180px;\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {\n    .layout_img_inner {\n        min-height: 200px;\n        min-width: 200px;\n    }\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n    .layout_img_inner {\n        min-height: 260px;\n    }\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 500px) {\n    .layout_img_inner {\n        min-height: 200px;\n    }\n\n\n}\n\n\nh1 {\n    font-family: 華康古印體;\n    font-size: 70px;\n}\n\nhr {\n    border: 2px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\n    opacity: .9;\n\n    align-items: center;\n}\n\n.layout_grid_inner {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    grid-gap: 2rem;\n}\n\n.layout_book {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;\n    grid-gap: 1rem;\n\n\n}\n\n.bookcontent {\n    height: 300px;\n    text-align: left;\n    margin-bottom: 5rem;\n}\n\nh2 {\n    font-size: 40px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\na {\n    color: black !important;\n    text-decoration: none !important;\n    display: flex !important;\n    border: 1px transparent !important;\n    transition: 0.3s !important;\n\n}\n\np {\n    height: fit-content;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    line-height: 36px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n}\n\n.book {\n    width: 200px;\n    padding: 0;\n    transiti